OL,3,C'We did it': Pitbull sets record for
OL,4,Clargest gathering of people in bald
OL,5,Ccaps
OL,7,FPitbull has set the Guinness World
OL,8,FRecord for the largest gathering of
OL,9,Fpeople wearing bald caps.
OL,11,FThe Latin hip hop artist, 45, was
OL,12,Frecognised with the achievement after
OL,13,F22,141 fans were counted wearing the
OL,14,Fcaps ahead of his British Summer Time
OL,15,F(BST) headline set in Hyde Park on
OL,16,FFriday evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
