OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783820902
OL,3,C'We did it': Pitbull sets record for
OL,4,Clargest gathering of people in bald
OL,5,Ccaps
OL,7,FPitbull fans, known as Bald-es, rushed
OL,8,Fto the main stage in their bald caps
OL,9,Fat the festival in order to be counted
OL,10,Fas temperatures were forecast to hit
OL,11,F31C in the capital.
OL,13,FMany sported the singer's signature
OL,14,Fblack aviators and stick on black
OL,15,Fgoatees, juggling pints of drink as
OL,16,Fthey carried inflatable globes.
OL,18,FThe festival organisers filmed the
OL,19,Fmoment the count was taken.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
