OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783820902
OL,3,C'We did it': Pitbull sets record for
OL,4,Clargest gathering of people in bald
OL,5,Ccaps
OL,7,FSpeaking before his certificate was
OL,8,Fpresented, Pitbull said: "Record-
OL,9,Fbreaking, record-making, history in
OL,10,Fthe making.
OL,12,F"Thank you London, thank you to the
OL,13,Ffans, thank you Hyde Park, thank you
OL,14,Fto the Bald-es."
OL,16,FThe musician, real name Armando
OL,17,FChristian Perez, was presented with
OL,18,Fthe framed Guinness World Record
OL,19,Fcertificate by BBC Radio 1 presenter
OL,20,FGreg James who suggested the idea
OL,21,Fearlier this year.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUtD@AOUvD@PO]
