CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783820902
OL,3,C'We did it': Pitbull sets record for
OL,4,Clargest gathering of people in bald
OL,5,Ccaps
OL,7,FAfter an official from the Guinness
OL,8,FWorld Records announced the number,
OL,9,FPitbull shouted, "We did it Bald-es,
OL,10,Fwe did it Bald-es."
OL,12,FAsked how he felt, the musician said:
OL,13,F"Tell you what I'm speechless at this
OL,14,Fpoint but I can tell you this much, I
OL,15,Fsay it to the Bald-es all the time in
OL,16,Fthe shows, when y'all put on them bald
OL,17,Fcaps you know you're about to have the
OL,18,Ftime of your life and now you're
OL,19,Fofficially in the Guinness book of
OL,20,FWorld Records."
OL,26,@qD@ROUrD@SO]uD@AOU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
