OL,3,C'We did it': Pitbull sets record for
OL,4,Clargest gathering of people in bald
OL,5,Ccaps
OL,7,FPitbull set the record as the first
OL,8,Fperson to attempt the feat under
OL,9,Fofficial adjudication, meaning there
OL,10,Fwas no previous record to beat.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FHe continued: "It's a blessing. It's
OL,18,Fan honour.
OL,26,@yD@OOU
