OL,3,C'We did it': Pitbull sets record for
OL,4,Clargest gathering of people in bald
OL,5,Ccaps
OL,7,F"First of all, to all the Bald-es and
OL,8,Fall the fans out there, what an
OL,9,Fhonour, a blessing, and it's still
OL,10,Famazing to go around any city.
OL,12,F"See, there's nowhere I can hide at
OL,13,Fthis point anywhere in the world,
OL,14,Fbecause you know when I'm in your city
OL,15,Fat this point.
OL,17,F"So to all the Bald-es, without y'all,
OL,18,Flike I said before, there's no
OL,19,FPitbull, no movement, no revolution."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
