OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783820902
OL,3,C'We did it': Pitbull sets record for
OL,4,Clargest gathering of people in bald
OL,5,Ccaps
OL,7,FTowards the end of the show, Pitbull
OL,8,Fled the crowd on a singalong of
OL,9,FOasis's Wonderwall, which he said was
OL,10,Fhis way of thanking fans for helping
OL,11,Fhim set the record, while fans flung
OL,12,Ftheir bald caps in the air as
OL,13,Ffireworks exploded over the stage
OL,14,Fduring Give Me Everything, the final
OL,15,Fsong.
OL,17,FIt comes after fans began a trend of
OL,18,Fattending Pitbull's concerts dressing
OL,19,Fup as him, sporting suits, aviator
OL,20,Fglasses and bald caps.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
