OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783820902
OL,3,C'We did it': Pitbull sets record for
OL,4,Clargest gathering of people in bald
OL,5,Ccaps
OL,7,FThe trend has gone viral in recent
OL,8,Fyears, with videos of audience-packed
OL,9,Farenas full of bald cap wearing fans
OL,10,Fsinging his songs back at him.
OL,12,FPrior to Friday's gig, the singer and
OL,13,Ffestival organisers had appealed for
OL,14,Fvolunteers to count bald caps in the
OL,15,Fcrowd.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
