PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783820902
OL,3,C'We did it': Pitbull sets record for
OL,4,Clargest gathering of people in bald
OL,5,Ccaps
OL,7,FThe rapper is among the roster of all-
OL,8,Fmale main stage headliners performing
OL,9,Fat the festival this year, following
OL,10,Fon from shows by US band Maroon 5,
OL,11,Ffolk pop group Mumford And Sons and an
OL,12,Fupcoming set from Scottish singer
OL,13,FLewis Capaldi.
OL,15,FMiami-born Pitbull is best known for
OL,16,Fthe songs Fireball, Timber, Time Of
OL,17,FOur Lives, On The Floor, Give Me
OL,18,FEverything, Feel This Moment and Don't
OL,19,FStop The Party.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
